snippet.title: Agent LovesD Visual Update - v2.00
snippet.description:
Agent LovesD is a Stealth Action Game about LovesD, an 'A' Checker. You'll Join in a tournament, Invade a 'gay guild', and Spy men, everything on behalf of the bad villain Mr. Trumpson. Avoid battles and Don't Get caught or Be Prepared to face the Gaydar!

Get it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1054470/Agent_Lovesdick/
Get it on Itch.io: https://maledollstudio.itch.io/agent-lovesdick
